# Documentation Branding Standards

## üé® jbcom Brand Requirements

ALL documentation in jbcom repositories MUST follow the unified design system.

### Reference Document

See `docs/DESIGN-SYSTEM.md` for complete brand specifications.

### Color Palette (Dark Theme)

| Purpose | Hex |
|---------|-----|
| Background | `#0a0f1a` |
| Surface/Cards | `#111827` |
| Primary (Cyan) | `#06b6d4` |
| Secondary (Blue) | `#3b82f6` |
| Text Primary | `#f1f5f9` |
| Text Secondary | `#94a3b8` |
| Success | `#10b981` |
| Warning | `#f59e0b` |
| Error | `#ef4444` |

### Typography

| Element | Font | Weight |
|---------|------|--------|
| Headings | Space Grotesk | 600-700 |
| Body | Inter | 400-500 |
| Code | JetBrains Mono | 400 |

## üìÅ Language-Specific Scaffolds

