## ‚úÖ Documentation Checklist

Before pushing documentation changes:

- [ ] Uses jbcom color palette (dark theme)
- [ ] Headings use Space Grotesk font
- [ ] Body text uses Inter font
- [ ] Code blocks use JetBrains Mono
- [ ] Links are cyan (`#06b6d4`)
- [ ] Code blocks have proper contrast
- [ ] Admonitions follow semantic colors
- [ ] Focus states are visible (accessibility)
- [ ] Meets WCAG AA contrast requirements

